<view class="page paw-memory-create-page safe-bottom">
  <view class="page-title">发布小爪记忆</view>
  <view class="page-desc">分享毛孩子今天的小瞬间，也保存那些值得记住的陪伴。</view>

  <view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="empty card">正在读取毛孩子档案...</view>
  <view wx:elif="{{loadFailed}}" class="empty card">暂时没有加载成功，请稍后再试。</view>
  <view wx:elif="{{cards.length === 0}}" class="empty card">
    <view>还没有可以选择的记忆卡，请先创建毛孩子档案。</view>
    <button class="primary-button empty-button" bindtap="goCreateCard">创建毛孩子档案</button>
  </view>

  <block wx:else>
    <view class="form-card card">
      <view class="field">
        <text class="form-label">选择毛孩子</text>
        <picker class="pet-picker-host" range="{{cards}}" range-key="pet_name" value="{{selectedCardIndex}}" bindchange="changePet">
          <view class="pet-picker">
            <image class="pet-avatar" src="{{selectedCard.photo_src}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
            <view>
              <view class="pet-name">{{selectedCard.pet_name}}</view>
              <view class="pet-meta">{{selectedCard.pet_type_label}} · {{selectedCard.pet_status_label}}</view>
            </view>
          </view>
        </picker>
      </view>

      <view class="field">
        <text class="form-label">写下今天的小瞬间</text>
        <textarea
          class="form-control textarea"
          value="{{content}}"
          maxlength="300"
          placeholder="写下它今天的小表情、小动作，或一个想保存的瞬间。"
          bindinput="inputContent"
        ></textarea>
        <view class="count-text">{{content.length}}/300</view>
      </view>

      <view class="field">
        <text class="form-label">上传照片或视频</text>
        <view class="field-help">图片或视频二选一。可以不上传媒体，但必须填写文字。</view>
        <view wx:if="{{mediaPath && mediaType === 'image'}}" class="media-box">
          <image class="media-preview" src="{{mediaPath}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
          <button class="quiet-button remove-media" bindtap="removeMedia">重新选择</button>
        </view>
        <view wx:elif="{{mediaPath && mediaType === 'video'}}" class="media-box">
          <video class="media-preview" src="{{mediaPath}}" controls object-fit="contain"></video>
          <view class="video-tip">{{videoDuration}} 秒</view>
          <button class="quiet-button remove-media" bindtap="removeMedia">重新选择</button>
        </view>
        <view wx:else class="media-actions">
          <button class="quiet-button media-button" bindtap="choosePhoto">选择照片</button>
          <button class="quiet-button media-button" bindtap="chooseVideo">选择视频</button>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="switch-row public-switch-row">
        <view>
          <view class="switch-title">申请公开展示</view>
          <view class="switch-desc">开启后进入审核，通过后会出现在公共小爪记忆。</view>
        </view>
        <switch color="#5B5F97" checked="{{visibility === 'pending'}}" bindchange="switchVisibility"></switch>
      </view>
    </view>

    <button class="primary-button submit-button" loading="{{submitting}}" bindtap="submitForm">{{visibility === 'pending' ? '提交公开审核' : '私密保存'}}</button>
  </block>
</view>
